title: BATTLE FOR THE BIG 10 & ACC
description:
Greg McElroy, Wendi Nix, and Desmond Howard talk about the battle in the state if Michigan for the BIG 10, also discuss potential outcomes of the ACC in a cluster at the top of the conference.
